 that Kokone\'s father told her as a mysterious fairy tale when she was little. (Source: ANN)',0),(1147,'24727','Baka to Test to Shoukanjuu Ni!: Mahou Hideyoshi Hideyoshi','https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/8/63597.jpg','PG-13 - Teens 13 or older','[\"Comedy\"]','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ReNteguUGUQ','A short special included on the second volume of Baka to Test to Shoukanjuu Ni! Blu-ray/DVD release.',0),(1148,'49613','Chiyu Mahou no Machigatta Tsukaikata: Senjou wo Kakeru Kaifuku Youin','https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1151/117193.jpg','PG-13 - Teens 13 or older','[\"Action\",\"Fantasy\"]',NULL,'Ken Usato is a normal high-schooler in every sense of the wordaverage grades, dreams, and a tendency to dislike extraordinary people. However, when he encounters the president and the vice president of the student council, both popular and extraordinary, he immediately befriends them. All of this is interrupted when Ken\'s new friends are summoned into another worldand he accidentally gets summoned as well! Dejected and with no way to return, he resigns himself to staying quietly in the new worlduntil he finds out he has an affinity for healing magic, a very rare form of magic which gives him both self-confidence and the attention of all mages. However, not all attention is good, which is something Ken realizes when he is noticed by a crazy fellow healing magic user... [Written by MAL Rewrite]',0),(1149,'9935','Chocolat no Mahou','https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/6/35601.jpg','PG-13 - Teens 13 or older','[\"Drama\",\"Supernatural\"]',NULL,'Chocolatier Chocolat Aikawa and her enigmatic acquaintance Cacao Theobroma run a shop named Chocolat Noir, which is famous for its specially crafted chocolates, known to miraculously grant wishes. A variety of troubled individuals find themselves in front of the shop, seeking its merchandise, but these chocolates are expensiveeach customer must pay with their most precious belonging. Although Chocolat seems 